name: Angelcat and Friends Collection – Danny Dog
description:
Angel Cat and Friends is about Cheonsa the Cat, an angel cat sent to earth to help fellow animals do good deeds. To disguise herself and do her mission, Cheonsa runs Coffee Cat, a café that caters to all animals in town. Her most frequent customers are Danny Dog, Rita Rabbit, Paulie Penguin, Chase Chick, Owen Owl and Barry Bear. Each of them has his/her own likes and dislikes as well as good and bad traits. With her yummy food and drinks, little pieces of advice and some help with their needs, Cheonsa inspires them to become better versions of themselves. This NFT is one of Cheonsa's friends and café customers, Danny Dog.

Danny Dog is an overworked employee of a small company. Because he is often dog-tired, he is often grouchy, stingy and complains even about the smallest of things. He goes to the café to relax after a hard day’s work. However, he works really hard. He is also knowledgeable about a lot of things. His sincerity and loyalty are unquestionable.
